      "firm_id": "detailed_1",
      "description": "This vehicle is in fair condition and serves as a reliable daily driver, though it does show its age. The exterior has several noticeable scratches and a small dent on the rear passenger door, while the interior upholstery has some staining and minor tears. Mechanically, the car starts and runs, but the suspension is beginning to feel a bit loose and it will likely need new tires and a brake service in the near future. It\u2019s a solid option for someone looking for basic transportation who doesn't mind putting in a little work to freshen it up.",
