    {
      "id": "sybil_1_listing_1",
      "firm_id": "sybil_1",
      "description": "Hey there! I\u2019m looking to find a new home for my trusty ride. It\u2019s been such a reliable companion and is still in really solid shape, ready for many more miles of adventures! It\u2019s super clean, well-loved, and drives like a dream. I\u2019m honestly a bit sad to see it go, but I know the next owner is going to have a blast with it. Come take it for a spin and see for yourself!",
